data.description: Super cute home on quiet culdesac in Springville! This adorable home has a great fenced lot, newer exterior and interior paint and features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms on the main level! Also, you will find an eat-in kitchen with an additional space for formal dining, new stainless appliances, beautiful vinyl laminate and beautiful neutral paint colors throughout. Outside you will find that the home has a low maintenance metal roof and a great area for kids and pets in the large yards. Home qualifies for USDA loan with zero down payment! Kitchen appliances will remain as well as washer and dryer. Septic tank cleaned 2020.
